description: The FTSE MIB Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Italian blue chip companies listed in EUR on the Borsa Italiana The 40 largest and most liquid companies Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Quarterly index review, largest component capped at 15% Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.ftse.com
